@startuml
title APEX-UPI Observability Architecture (Read-only)

actor Operator

package "TPAP" {
  [TPAP]
}

package "Business Flow" {
  [Kafka] as Kafka
  [Transaction Orchestrator] as Orchestrator
  [NPCI Adapter] as NpciAdapter
  [NPCI] as Npci
  [Webhook] as Webhook
  [Ledger]
}

package "Dashboard" {
  package "dashboard-ui" {
    [Executive Overview]
    [Live Transaction Monitor]
    [Kafka Monitoring Center]
    [Reconciliation / Ledger / Audit / Errors / Health]
  }
}

package "Read-only Observability API" {
  [operations-dashboard-api]
  [Monitoring-only Kafka consumers]
  [Read-only PostgreSQL queries]
}

Operator --> "dashboard-ui" : View

TPAP --> Kafka
Kafka --> Orchestrator
Orchestrator --> Kafka
Kafka --> NpciAdapter
NpciAdapter --> Npci
Npci --> Webhook
Webhook --> Ledger

Kafka ..> "operations-dashboard-api" : monitoring-only consumption (groups like dashboard-monitor-group)
Ledger ..> "operations-dashboard-api" : read-only

@enduml

